commentary: Chatara to Phehlukwayo, OUT to the keeper! Phehlukwayo goes for a duck. Length ball going across his body, and he tried to push at it. Beaten by the pace, and it takes an outside edge to the keeper

commentary: Chatara to Steyn, FOUR runs driven straight past the bowler! And South Africa make it three-nil. Length ball outside off, and thumped to the left of the bowler
